CategoryName: Category Name is an alphanumeric text field which does not have any character limits or field length limits.  All names in this field should be created as Categories for GL numbers to be assigned to.  This is the list that is referenced against on the GL Account Upload file.
IntegrationPackage: This is a required field.  This field is a text field and is compared for an exact match in the system.  If no exact match is found, the row will be marked invalid.  To find the integration package name, refer to the Integration Package field on any Active Property in Property Setup.
